data.description: Wonderfully located home nestled on a private dead-end street in the Northeast quadrant of Twin Falls.  SELLER IS OFFERING A FULL CARPET REPLACEMENT AT CLOSING! Just minutes from major shopping, schools, parks & the canyon rim walking trail. This home offers privacy, ample natural light, and a wonderful backyard with a spacious covered back patio. The primary suite offers direct access to the back patio, dual vanity, & spacious closet space. The living room is open to the efficiently laid out kitchen & dining room, spacious & perfect for entertaining with a gas fireplace, perfect for curling up with a good book. The second bedroom is roomy with a walk-in closet & a sweet bay window, currently set up as a reading nook. The furnace was replaced about 4 years ago, and the AC unit was replaced within the last 1.5 years. HOA dues cover common area landscape/tree maintenance of the neighborhood entrance.
